style: normal;\">Remember</em>, les parachutistes de la France Libre ‚Äì 1940 √† 1943</p>\r\n<div id=\"ftn2\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_ftn2\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref2\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn2;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[2]</span></span></a> Le BCRAM sera cr√©e en janvier 1942</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn1\" href=\"#_ftnref1\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[3]</span></span></a> Source¬†: lettre de Gilbert Mus en mai 2005.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn2\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_ftn2\" href=\"#_ftnref2\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn2;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[4]</span></span></a> Malade, le capitaine Jean Lambert est rest√© au Caire et rejoint quelques semaines plus tard. De m√™me, souffrant, le sous-lieutenant Jacquier a √©t√© hospitalis√© √† Cape Town et rejoindra le 1<sup>er</sup> BIA en ao√ªt.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn3\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_ftn3\" href=\"#_ftnref3\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn3;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[5]</span></span></a> Voir les notes de service cit√©es par R. Flamand dans ¬´¬†Qui Ose Gagne ‚Äì Les Parachutistes de la France libre 3<sup>e</sup> SAS 1943-1944¬†¬ª</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn4\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn4\" href=\"#_ftnref4\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn4;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[6]</span></span></a> Allocution du brigadier Mc Leod d√©but 1944 aux SAS fran√ßais (source¬†: document du Lt J. Ferchaud)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn5\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 120%;\"><a name=\"_ftn5\" href=\"#_ftnref5\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn5;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[7]</span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt;\"> Rapport en date de juin 1944 du g√©n√©ral Valin de l‚ÄôEtat-major des FAFL en Grande-Bretagne ‚Äì Source SHA Vincennes</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>¬†</p>\r\n<div id=\"ftn1\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_ftn1\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref1\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[8]</span></span></a> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Les √©quipes Jedburgh d√©pendent du SFHQ et sont compos√©es pour les missions en France d‚Äôun officier fran√ßais, d‚Äôun officier am√©ricain ou britannique et d‚Äôun op√©rateur radio. Elles sont charg√©es d‚Äôarmer et instruire les r√©sistants, de transmettre les informations et de coordonner les actions de sabotage.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn2\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn2\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref2\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn2;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[9]</span></span></a> Voir l‚Äô√©tude de Y. Lagadec dans ¬´¬†La r√©sistance bretonne vue par les forces sp√©ciales alli√©es¬†¬ª</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn3\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn3\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref3\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn3;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[10]</span></span></a> Cit√© par Roger Flamand dans ¬´¬†Les parachutistes de la France libre 3<sup>e</sup> SAS 1943-1944¬†¬ª</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn4\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn4\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref4\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn4;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[11]</span></span></a> Le 3 juillet, des √©l√©ments du squadron B du 1<sup>st</sup> SAS Regiment sont attaqu√©s √† leur base du bois de Verri√®res. 31 prisonniers sont ex√©cut√©s le 7 juillet.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ftn5\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a name=\"_ftn5\" href=\"index.php?view=article&amp;id=189%3Ales-2e-et-3e-rcp-creation-formation-emploi&amp;task=edit&amp;ret=aHR0cDovL2ZmbHNhcy5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fY29udGVudCZ2aWV3PWFydGljbGUmaWQ9MTg5Omxlcy0yZS1ldC0zZS1yY3AtLWNyZWF0aW9uLWZvcm1hdGlvbi1lbXBsb2kmY2F0aWQ9Mzg6ZXZlbmVtZW50cyZsYW5nPWZy&amp;option=com_content&amp;lang=fr#_ftnref5\" style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn5;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\">[12]</span></span></a> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Lettre de Mc Leod √† Conan en date du 5/09/1944</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"mso-element: footnote-list;\">\r\n<p>¬†</p>\r\n<p>¬†</p>\r\n<p>¬†</p>\r\n</div>', '2013-09-29 12:14:48', '62', 'fr');
