01pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ouvrages:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span>Remember, les parachutistes de la France libre, Raymond Forgeat, Ed. SHAT 1990.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm -14.5pt 0.0001pt 0cm; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">B√©rets rouges en Indochine, La ¬Ω Brigade SAS, Raymond Muelle, Presse de la Cit√©, Ed. 1986.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span>Histoire des parachutistes fran√ßais, Direction Paul Gaugac, Editions Albatros, </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ed. 1975, volume double 1 & 2.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">¬© JF Bianchi 02-2010<span> </span>-<span> </span><a href=\"mailto:jf.bianchi@wanadoo.fr\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">jf.bianchi@wanadoo.fr</span></a></span></p>\n<p>¬†</p>', '2010-08-22 07:01:05', '1566', 'fr');
